### Get all items (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get all items (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items?_page=1&_limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get item by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/5 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Create item
POST http://localhost:5000/api/items HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": "Headphones",
  "amount": 2,
  "price": 500,
  "shop": "Comfy",
  "measure": "unit",
  "currency": "UAH"
}

### Update item
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/items/5 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": "Laptop",
  "amount": 1,
  "price": 850.00,
  "shop": "Comfy",
  "measure": "unit",
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Delete item
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/items/5 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json